name: "fear"
description:
It was strange, since morning that i’ve started drawing this character I felt strange but I can’t say exactly how I felt. it was something like fear or maybe stress. well, I don’t even know .
these days I have severe difficulties , I'm worried about my family and friends which are in the middle of the war . sadly I couldn’t be in touch with them like 4 or 5 days . another thing is the emptiness in my heart again I can’t find the right words to explain it . this picture may be the explanation of my mute emptiness .
